{"tid":606802,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"川普下令驅逐60名俄羅斯人","createTime":"2018-03-26T18:03:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-27T00:15:19.000Z","uid":41818,"like":6,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e188baecd39a6370084b007563a09535d67169e4","tid":606802,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T18:03:44.000Z","msg":"川普總統週一下令驅逐60名俄羅斯人，作為對俄羅斯涉嫌毒害在英國的前俄羅斯間諜一事的回應。60人中包括12名被認定為駐紐約聯合國的俄羅斯情報人員。<br />\n<br />\n驅逐令還包括關閉俄羅斯駐西雅圖的領事館。官員稱，俄羅斯人及其家屬需在七天內離開美國。<br />\n<br />\n這個驅逐令是川普總統對克里姆林宮採取的最強硬行動，此前川普一直被批評對俄羅斯總統普丁不夠強硬。<br />\n<br />\n在與記者的通話中，白宮高級官員表示，此舉是為了剷除積极參与對美國情報活動的俄羅斯人，並表明美國將與北約盟國站在一起。官員稱，西雅圖領事館被關閉是因為其靠近一處美國海軍基地。<br />\n<br />\n英國此前曾將23名俄羅斯外交官驅逐，使兩國之間的緊張局勢升溫至冷戰以來的最高水平。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://cn.nytimes.com/world/20180326/trump-russia-diplomats-expulsion/zh-hant/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcn.nytimes.com%2Fworld%2F20180326%2Ftrump-russia-diplomats-expulsion%2Fzh-hant%2F&d=f%2BmPlfixWRiD26j9HppfkUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=852ae9cb\" target=\"_blank\">https://cn.nytimes.com/world/20180326/trump-russia-diplomats-expulsion/zh-hant/</a>"},{"pid":"195eebabde2f17b627659f48ec6d3735ba56071d","tid":606802,"uid":4783,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T18:04:42.000Z","msg":"trump又通俄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3532b089eed8169a535467ad318f03d16cd50036","tid":606802,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"195eebabde2f17b627659f48ec6d3735ba56071d","tid":606802,"uid":4783,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T18:04:42.000Z","msg":"trump又通俄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T18:56:59.000Z","msg":"一定係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n扮關係差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc7bb3f3a3dc6e6f0316988cdde6266b984a7aea","tid":606802,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T23:33:02.000Z","msg":"打WW3<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3abd95499464829431527c836997737475207e71","tid":606802,"uid":48358,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T00:09:53.000Z","msg":"睇睇吓變左殘體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"857cbbf143d249663ad4e1fcd52fbde89ba67e3a","tid":606802,"uid":3068,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T00:15:19.000Z","msg":"殘體冇可信性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}